                       *** System global variables ***

Use the PONS command to list them.

Fixed at boot:
	$num_colours
	$degs_per_rad
	$file_extension
	$pic_file_extension
	$interpreter
	$e
	$pi
	$copyright
	$version
	$build_date
	$username
	$pid
	$home

Can changa during run:
	$win_height
	$win_width
	$win_colour
	$angle_mode
	$winpic
